node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on August 12, 2021 tagging @langleav. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'The Only Thing You Can Do The man who says sorry when he hurts you is redeemable. The one who would never make that mistake in the first place is admirable. But the man who perpetually fails to acknowledge his cannot take a minor blow to his ego to soothe and assure you the only thing you can do with this man is walk away. -LANG LEAV'.

node.text:
I love this piece of advice ✨⠀
(cr: @langleav)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by poets of instagram on August 10, 2021 tagging @poetryofdhiman. May be an image of text that says 'You have to believe in yourself. You have to try again and again. Not for anyone else but for yourself. No matter how things went in the past, no matter how many times you have failed to overcome the obstacles on your path, remember you have this far and you stronger than ever. While things still do not always turn out the way you want, I hope through all of this you are learning to find that with belief in the heart nothing is impossible to conquer. come are -DHIMAN'.
